div.p: Build a system to support Car Rental service for an shop owner
It should support multiple type of vehicle

There can be variety of vehicle under same category like: Scooter -> Motor scooter or CNG scooter -> Both can come in multiple size
There can be bicycle also in vehicle which does not have unique registration number
Capability Required for:
Owner to manage Inventory
User should be able to rent vehicle
Cost calculation

div.div:
API:
Add vehicle cost
POST: rental/service/v1/vehicle/cost
{
"category": "Scooter/Car/Cycle", //mandatory
"size": "S/M/L", //optional
"subCategory": "CNG/Motor", // optional
"unit": "Day/Month/ Hr", //mandatory
"cost": 200 // mandatory
}
Update vehicle cost
POST: rental/service/v1/vehicle/cost
{
"vc_id":12, //mandatory
"category": "Scooter/Car/Cycle", //mandatory
"size": "S/M/L", //optional
"subCategory": "CNG/Motor", // optional
"unit": "Day/Month/ Hr", //mandatory
"cost": 200 // mandatory
}
Add vehicle
POST: rental/service/v1/vehicle
{
"vehicleNbr": "123ABC", //Optional
"category": "Scooter/Car/Cycle", //mandatory
"size": "S/M/L", //optional
"subCategory": "CNG/Motor", // optional
"manufacturingDate": "", //optional
"status": "AVAILABLE/UNDER_MAINTANENCE/DISCARDED", //mandatory
"cost": 200, // optional
"unit": "Day/Month/ Hr", //optional
"qty": 10 //optional default take 1 qty
}
ResponseBody : { "v_id":12} Status: 201
